cs.MA, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.RO 

The paper discusses experimental verification of stability in multi-agent reinforcement learning algorithms, which falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA). The paper also discusses the use of metrics to assess the convergence of these algorithms, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also touches on the control and optimization of these systems (cs.SY) and the use of robotics in multi-agent systems (cs.RO).
